# The box image builds from the repo root but needs only the engine inputs:
# npm manifests, research-workflow sources, and box files. Everything else
# stays out of the build context (target/ alone is gigabytes).
*
!package.json
!package-lock.json
!packages/
!packages/research-workflow/
!packages/research-workflow/package.json
!packages/research-workflow/tsconfig.json
!packages/research-workflow/schemas/
!packages/research-workflow/schemas/**
!packages/research-workflow/src/
!packages/research-workflow/src/**
!box/
box/Dockerfile
